(5, '4', 'Ranjit Kumar Ray', '01719480292', 'rkray86@gmail.com', 'Dear Sir,\r\nThis is Ranjit Kumar Ray. I’m writing to submit my application for the open \" Assistant Manager /Manager \" role in the Transmission department. \r\n \r\nI’m an graduate with Bsc degree in Electrical & Electronic Engineering from Eastern University. I have twelve  years working experience in the telecom industry. I have working experience as a MW Transmission Manager at GrameenPhone Ltd, Robi Axiata Ltd & Banglalink  Digital Communication Ltd via Tech360 Ltd.\r\n \r\nI hope my resume convinces you that I’m a diligent, reliable candidate.\r\n \r\nThank you for considering my application. I look forward to hearing from you.\r\n \r\nSincerely,\r\nRanjit Kumar Ray \r\nCell : +8801719480292\r\n        +8801601480292', 'adminAssets/upload/1701516368467.pdf', 'yes', '2023-12-02 05:26:08', '2023-12-02 05:26:08'),
(6, '6', 'Md Hasibuzzaman Shakil', '01777251762', 'hasibuzzamanshakil@gmail.com', 'December 04, 2023\r\nTo \r\nHuman Resource Manager\r\nOne Sky Communications Limited\r\n115, 23 Toyenbee Circular Road, Dhaka 1000\r\nSubject: Application for the position of “Store Keeper”\r\n\r\nDear Sir,\r\nIn response to your job advertisement published in One Sky Website December 04 2023. I would like to introduce myself to you as I believe I have the skills, qualifications, and experience necessary to make a significant contribution to your organization.\r\n\r\nI am completed my Diploma-in-Engineering degree from the Department of Electrical Engineering of Rajshahi Polytechnic Institute. My keen interest in Electrical and Electronic Engineering has enabled me to develop a good knowledge of electrical power, circuit, control, safety and IT.\r\n\r\nI have Four years of experience in Installing, Maintenance, Troubleshooting of Computer Hardware and operating systems. That enhanced my technical capacity and performance. However, I can assure you that I am a quick learner, adaptive as well as an energetic person.\r\nDuring my six months of experience with Microsoft Office, I have gained proficiency in using applications such as Word, Excel, and PowerPoint. I have successfully created and formatted documents, utilized advanced functions and formulas in Excel for data analysis, and designed visually appealing presentations using PowerPoint\'s features.\r\n\r\nI believe working in a reputed organization like your one will provide me an excellent opportunity for my career. I would truly be grateful if I was finally selected for that post and I will prove myself to be an important asset for your company through my dedication, sincerity and highest level of professionalism.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nMd. Hasibuzzaman Shakil\r\nCell no: +8801777-251762\r\nE mail: hasibuzzamanshakil@gmail.com', 'adminAssets/upload/1701703301187.pdf', 'yes', '2023-12-04 09:21:41', '2023-12-04 09:21:41'),
(8, '3', 'Ratul Bin Nazrul Antor', '01944554421', 'ratulantor444@gmail.com', 'Ratul Bin Nazrul Antor\r\n01944554421 | ratulantor444@gmail.com | Gazipur, Bangladesh\r\n\r\nJan 02, 2024\r\n\r\nDear Hiring Manager,\r\n\r\nMy name is Ratul Bin Nazrul Antor and I\'m writing this letter to express my interest in the position of Sales & Marketing Sr.Executive at One Sky Communications Limited . I\'m an IT professional with over 5 years of experience working with systems that range from ISP to business solutions. I\'m familiar with your company and am impressed by the dependability of the technological solutions that you offer to your clients. I\'m excited about the opportunity to contribute to your team\'s success with my experience and expertise.\r\n\r\nI have a diploma degree in computer science. In my most recent role, I worked as an IT professional responsible for maintaining the company\'s servers. In this capacity, I worked with various teams that handled customers. I\'ve also worked as a customer support specialist where I supported clients who were facing technical difficulties. Throughout my career, I\'ve worked with many different marketplace and with different shapes and sizes.\r\n\r\nI believe that my qualifications make me an ideal candidate for this position, and I\'m excited about the opportunity to work with such an impressive company. I\'ve attached a copy of my resume with this letter, along with one professional reference for you to contact. If you have any questions about my application, please don\'t hesitate to contact me via phone or email. I look forward to the opportunity to discuss this role with you further.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nRatul Bin Nazrul Antor', 'adminAssets/upload/1704192417859.pdf', 'yes', '2024-01-02 04:46:57', '2024-01-02 04:46:57'),
(9, '3', 'SHEIKH SHAWON', '01774266507', 'sheikhshawon980@gmail.com', 'To work for an organization using my knowledge and potentials that I have acquired from my academic & professional experience to achieve best results and to value my post together with initiative ideas. My ultimate aim is to work as an active member of an energetic team in a large environment so that I can exploit my full potential.', 'adminAssets/upload/1704216453497.docx', 'yes', '2024-01-02 11:27:33', '2024-01-02 11:27:33'),
(10, '6', 'Farukh Ahmed', '01617846669', 'farukhahmed32joy@gmail.com', 'I hope you are well.\r\nWishing you good health and Well-being.\r\n\r\nWith due respect, I am Farukh Ahmed, I have come to know through BD Jobs Online published on 08 January, 2024 that Application for post of Store Keeper will be appointed under you. I am applying as an interested candidate for the said post. For your kind information I have attached my resume.\r\n\r\nTherefore, it is my earnest request to Sir that if you appoint me to the said post, I will always strive to satisfy you with my honesty and hard work.\r\n\r\nWith best regards \r\n\r\nFarukh Ahmed', 'adminAssets/upload/1705333690339.pdf', 'yes', '2024-01-15 09:48:10', '2024-01-15 09:48:10'),
(11, '8', 'Md Fuad Hasan', '01689543316', 'fuadhasan.connect@gmail.com', 'Date:  28 January 2024\r\n\r\nTo\r\nThe Head of the Human Resource Division\r\n \r\nSubject: Application for the position of Jr. Executive - IT\r\n \r\nDear Sir,\r\nI am writing concerning the position of  Jr. Executive - IT   in your organization. I have a particular interest in working for your organization and would appreciate being considered as a candidate for employment. I can make a positive contribution to your company.\r\n\r\nI have completed Bachelor of Science at Eastern University, Bangladesh in Computer Science and Engineering. I can work effectively under pressure and handle my time efficiently. I have developed excellent communication skills through my working experience and campus leadership roles.\r\n\r\nMy Curriculum Vitae and photo are attached. I appreciate your consideration of my credentials. If I can provide you with additional information, please let me know. You can reach me by email at fuadhasan.connect@gmail.com or by phone at +8801689-543316. I look forward to discussing about my qualifications with you in person.\r\n\r\n\r\nSincerely\r\nMd. Fuad Hasan', 'adminAssets/upload/1706460158697.pdf', 'yes', '2024-01-28 10:42:39', '2024-01-28 10:42:39');

